00:04:27.596 --> 00:04:28.440
So what do I do?

00:04:28.440 --> 00:04:31.760
I take [1, 2], and I
multiply it by [2, 1].

00:04:31.760 --> 00:04:34.570
So I take 1 times
2, plus 2 times 1.

00:04:34.570 --> 00:04:40.290
So I get 2 there and
2 there, so I get a 4.

00:04:40.290 --> 00:04:43.970
And then the next
