00:04:50.420 --> 00:04:52.010
And then the last column.

00:04:52.010 --> 00:04:53.620
1 times 3 is 3.

00:04:53.620 --> 00:04:55.200
2 times 4 is 8.

00:04:55.200 --> 00:04:59.230
So I get 3 plus 8, so I get 11.

00:04:59.230 --> 00:05:02.980
